name: InspiringEntrepreneurs
0:
”Alexa, open Inspiring entrepreneurs”
”Alexa, start Inspiring entrepreneurs”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: inspiring entrepreneurs
des:
Discover phrases that value the entrepreneurial culture.

Listen to phrases about technology, questions that involve creating a business, entrepreneurship in the environment in which it operates, reflections on the daily lives of those who already undertake, or provocations for those who are thinking of entrepreneurship and dive into concepts and practices in the world of entrepreneurship.

To begin with, just say "Alexa, open Inspiring entrepreneurs" or "Alexa, start Inspiring entrepreneurs" to receive a sentence.

At any time, you can say "Alexa, stop".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
